---
import navigatorImage from "../assets/img/CUREO5/CUREO-Therapie-Navigator.jpg";
---

<section class="modules" data-reveal>
  <div class="modules-shell">
    <article class="modules-grid">
      <div class="modules-content">
        <p class="eyebrow">MODULES AND USE CASES</p>
        <h2>Understanding CUREO, Modules and Areas of Application</h2>
        <p>
          CUREO offers exercises to improve fine and gross motor skills,
          sensory perception (e.g. spatial awareness), and cognition (e.g.
          memory, attention). All content can be adapted to the individual
          needs of each patient.
        </p>
        <p>
          Complementary tests such as reaction, precision or reach support
          therapy monitoring. Diagnostic use is explicitly excluded. CUREO
          targets sensorimotor, cognitive, and perceptual impairments.
        </p>
        <p>
          The high-frequency, immersive therapy with multimodal feedback has a
          positive effect on neuronal processes, supporting the recovery of
          motor and cognitive abilities as well as the improvement of sensory
          functions - ultimately enhancing everyday capabilities. Increased
          motivation through gamification, rapidly visible training progress,
          and active relaxation tools all contribute to therapeutic success.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="modules-media">
        <img
          src={navigatorImage.src}
          alt="CUREO therapy navigator interface and VR exercise overview"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .modules {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f1f3ee 0%, #f8fcf2 100%);
    padding: 0 1.2rem 2rem;
  }

  .modules-shell {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 1240px;
  }

  .modules-grid {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 165, 59, 0.34);
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(88, 126, 50, 0.1);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(360px, 1.1fr) minmax(320px, 1fr);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .modules-content {
    align-self: center;
    padding: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: #688247;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin: 0 0 0.55rem;
  }

  .modules-content h2 {
    color: #1d2f1d;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.7vw, 2.2rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .modules-content p {
    color: #425641;
    line-height: 1.56;
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
  }

  .modules-media {
    min-height: 420px;
  }

  .modules-media img {
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    width: 100%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .modules-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .modules-media {
      max-height: 420px;
      min-height: 300px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .modules {
      padding: 0 0.8rem 1.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>
